    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the corn is in the oven, peel your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Cut your<strong> green chilli[es]</strong> in half and deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon)</p><p>Peel and halve your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Cut your<strong> pepper[s]</strong> into quarters (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon)</p>",
