    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>garlic </strong>to a <strong>food processor </strong>with most<strong> </strong>of your <strong>coriander </strong>(reserve a few leaves for garnish!), the <strong>halved</strong> <strong>chilli[es]</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>half </strong>of the <strong>shallot[s] </strong>and <strong>pepper quarters</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>toasted sesame seeds </strong>and <strong>pumpkin seeds</strong>, season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and blitz into a rough paste – this is your <strong>pepper paste</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1718791312671-x200.jpg",
