    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>free range chicken breast portion[s]</strong> and cook for 3 min on each side or until golden</p><p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> and <strong>creamed coconut</strong> in 200ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[260ml]</span> [300ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>coconut stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
